Attention Please

Before I tell you anything about this model, I must tell you to check out Babes - Babes 2.0 | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

It's a great checkpoint and the ver2 was released! Go download it and support its creator, he's nice and worked hard for months to train it!

Street Fashion

This model aims to give you more options for chic street fashion, it's very creative and I encourage you to be adventurous, yet reasonable, with prompts.

Take what I used as a base and develop on it.
